snippet.title: Cataclysm Wars Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Cataclysm Wars is now on Steam! 

The Empire is under attack, and only its mighty armies can save it! Shame you aren't in charge of those, then. Lead an outmatched militia through overwhelming odds in this turn-based strategy game, and save your nation from collapse. Or, lead the dogged Syrinx foe and crush the Empire!

Wishlist or follow us here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3405960/Cataclysm_Wars/
